CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 29, 1952, pg. 1 reads: "Happy Moments in Lives Of These "Favorite Churchwomen" - These five contestants shared honors last Thursday night in A. Leo Weil School Auditorium...Extreme right: the Rev. A. A. Nelson is given a check for $25 from his contestant, Mrs. Odessa Bussey, fifth prize winner..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of P.L. Prattis, Rev. A.A. Nelson holding check with Odessa Bussey, with P.L. Prattis and Jessie Vann looking on, standing at podium in A. Leo Weil school during "Favorite Churchwoman's" contest award program
